  * Bug fix: "erc: cannot connect to Undernet", thanks to Frederic Roussel
    (Closes: #282003).
  * Bug fix: "erc: erc-nickserv fails everything when server name contains
    digits", thanks to Pietro Giorgianni (Closes: #266347).
